title: Dakine Laurel 20L Pack
description:
Check out 360° views of the 2014 Womens Laurel pack in Wellington.
Laurel pack Features: 
- Button magnet closure
- Braided vinyl drawstring
- Vinyl logo and trims
- Adjustable web shoulder straps
- Metal hardware
- Exterior organizer pocket
- Interior zippered pocket
- Polyester lining
